body.p:
While projects exist to provide information on ancient places (e.g., Pleiades gazetteer of ancient places; 
                http://pleiades.stoa.org/), and others make available repositories of searchable texts (e.g., Perseus Digital Library, 
                http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/), our aim is to bring text and geography together to produce a GIS tightly integrated with our growing collection of texts and standoff data.
